Package alix.util

Class IntIntMap

java.lang.Object
alix.util.IntIntMap
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable
public class IntIntMap
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
An efficient int-int Map implementation, encoded in a long array for key and value. A special method is used to modify a value by addition. Used for word vectors indexed by int. A local Cosine is implemented. Be careful, do not use -2147483648 as a key (Integer.MIN_VALUE), is used to tag empty value, no warning will be sent. source: http://java-performance.info/implementing-world-fastest-java-int-to-int-hash-map/
